ConditionDescription: A rare Hermes gem called President from the infamous Symbiose collection. Come with the Dust bag. As for the collection itself, consider President, a handled variation of a zippered envelope in a rich textural blend of black calf and black suede adorned in front with an eye-catching, free-form configuration of emerald green lizard. Characteristic of Hermes quality, the lining is handsome black Morocco leather. President is made of different leathers: Lizard, Suede, Calfskin, cowhide, etc. It is more of a conceptual bag with functional design. The green lizard on the front is so sharp and vibrant! Back in the time when the Symbiose was introduced, our beloved Hermes master craftman, Claude, visited five of Hermes boutiques in the States to show the crafting of a handbag. This President is in good used condition. Inside is clean. The suede has some rubbed wear.  Functionally it is solid and sound. This is a must have for you Hermes connoisseur! Bring this unique beauty home today!
